Filter

 LogWEx can be installed as a servlet filter in a Web Application. You should add this in WEB-INF/web.xml :

    <filter>
        <filter-name>logwex</filter-name>
        <filter-class>org.sewatech.logwex.MDCPreparerFilter</filter-class>
    </filter>

    <filter-mapping>
        <filter-name>logwex</filter-name>
        <url-pattern>*</url-pattern>
    </filter-mapping>
 
